# Anything Ben-or-others' real client matter folders. Filing folders typically
# contain confidential application content. The skill is meant to be RUN
# against such folders, not to bundle them — so they should never be in the
# repo. Common patterns:
FINAL - TO BE REVIEWED-SIGNED/
*MS-Matters/
*MS1-*/
*-CON/
*-Application.*
*-Specification.*
*-Drawings.*
*-ADS.*
*-Declaration.*
*-Assignment.*
